<div id="user_pc_bg" onclick="user_off(); return false;" style="position:fixed; left:0; top:0; width:100%; height:100%; z-index:1; display:none;"></div>
<div id="user_bg" onclick="user_off(); return false;" style="position:fixed; top:0; width:inherit; height:100%; background-color:#000; z-index:8; opacity:0.6; display:none;"></div>
<div id="user_overlay" style="width:inherit; position:fixed; top:48px; z-index:13; display:none; background:#f4f4f4;">
	<table class="main_header" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="position:fixed; top:0; background-color:#4b3d3d; width:inherit; overflow:visible; height:47px;">
		<tr>
			<td style="width:60px;">
			</td>
			<td style="text-align:center;">
				<a href="/" style="display:block; font-size:20px; color:#FFFFFF; margin:0 auto; margin-top:3px;">마이 페이지</a>
			</td>
			<td style="width:60px; position:relative;">
				<a href="#" onclick="user_off(); return false;"><img style="width:26px; padding:12px 10px; margin-bottom:-4px; margin-left:4px;" src="/images/header/menu_off.png" /></a>
				<img src="/images/etc/detail.png" style="position:absolute; right:18px; bottom:0; width:20px;">
			</td>
		</tr>
	</table>
	<div style="width:100%; background:#f4f4f4;">
		<div style="width:100%; text-align:left;">
			<p style="padding:18px 12px; margin:0;">
			 	<span style="color:#ee6e01;">@<%= current_user.string_id %></span>님, 환영합니다!
			 	<a href="/users/manage" style="float:right;"><img style="width:22px;" src="/images/common/setting_btn.png"></a>
			</p>
		</div>
		
		<div style="padding:50px 12px 16px 12px; margin:0; font-size:12px; color:#9d9ea0; text-align:left; line-height:22px;">
			<a href="#" onclick="alert('준비중입니다.')" style="color:#9d9ea0;"><span style="color:#988574; font-size:15px; font-weight:bold;">- ABOUT US :</span> 저희가 도대체 뭐하는 사람들이냐구요?</a><br />
			<a href="/etc/inquiry" style="color:#9d9ea0;"><span style="color:#988574; font-size:15px; font-weight:bold;">- CONTACT US :</span> 혹시 불편하신 점이 있으신가요? 말씀해주세요!</a> <br />
			<a href="#" onclick="alert('준비중입니다.')" style="color:#9d9ea0;"><span style="color:#988574; font-size:15px; font-weight:bold;">- AGREEMENT :</span> 당신의 소중한 개인정보, 이렇게 지켜드립니다!</a> <br />
			<a href="#" onclick="alert('준비중입니다.')" style="color:#9d9ea0;"><span style="color:#988574; font-size:15px; font-weight:bold;">- FAQ, HELP :</span> 사용법이 어려우신가요? 도와드리겠습니다!</a>
		</div>

		<div style="border-top:1px solid #dbdbdb; border-bottom:1px solid #dbdbdb; text-align:left; position:relative;">
			<div style="padding:30px 12px; margin:0;">
				<span style="display:inline-block; color:#393939; border-bottom:2px solid #9c9c9c; font-weight:bold; font-size:15px;">Offer Wanted</span>
				<p style="color:#383838; font-size:13px; line-height:20px;">
					함께 땀 흘릴 개발자 구인중!<br />
					열정 넘치는 인재를 모십니다!
				</p>

			</div>
			<img style="width:120px; position:absolute; right:30px; top:16px;" src="/images/etc/offer_wanted.png" />
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<script>
	<% if flash[:custom_notice] %>
		notify('<%=flash[:custom_notice]%>');
	<% end %>

	function user_on(){
		$("#user_overlay").show();
		$("#user_pc_bg").show();
		$("#user_bg").show();
	}

	function user_off(){
		$("#user_overlay").hide();
		$("#user_pc_bg").hide();
		$("#user_bg").hide();
	}

</script>
